CGI-Application-Plugin-I18N version 0.03
========================================

This module is a plugin to extend CGI::Application with I18N capabilities.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  I18N::LangTags
  Locale::Maketext::Simple
  CGI::Application
  
SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc CGI::Application::Plugin::I18N

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=CGI-Application-Plugin-I18N

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/CGI-Application-Plugin-I18N

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/CGI-Application-Plugin-I18N

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI-Application-Plugin-I18N


